title: Star Wars - Dark Times - Out of the Wilderness (01 - 05) (2011 -
description:
Star Wars - Dark Times - Out of the Wilderness (01 - 05) (2011 - 2012) (Minutemen-DarthGobbie)


Although just a 5 issue limited series, this series is a continuation of Star Wars: Dark Times, which itself was a continuation of Star Wars: Republic.

Even though a mini-series, this series continues to count on as Star Wars: Republic in the indica, making these issues 101 till 105 of Star Wars: Republic.
